summary: namgi, thirty thousand feet and falling
title: namgi, thirty thousand feet and falling
body:
title: thirty thousand feet and falling 

author: linzeigh @kimseokjinsthighs

pairing: namjoon/yoongi 

words: 16 608 

notes: non-idol au, alpha/beta/omega dynamics, strangers to lovers, smut 

summary: from twitter au idea: seat neighbor airplane au, omega yoongi is so fucking attracted to his seat neighbor’s smell that he accidentally starts leaking and alpha joon is like “you um… you - your smell? i think you…” to which yoongi promptly replies “fuck, oh my god”. 

“you’re so wet, yoongi, aren’t you worried about ruining another set of clothes, baby?” 

yoongi channels his sexual frustration into aggression, setting his jaw when he glares. “i hope your dick falls off after this.” 

“right. after this.” 

“i’m pissy, not stupid. fuck me.” 

probably the best abo au i ever read. i don’t enjoy these fics but this one? it’s really great. the characterization was on point and i loved interactions between namjoon and yoongi so much. it wasn’t just smut. it was funny, it was hilarious. and really good too.
